Turkish Watchdog Asks Banks for Growth Plan Details, HT Reports

-- B y   M a r k   B e n t l e y
-- 
2011-03-14T06:18:23Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-14/turkish-watchdog-asks-banks-for-growth-plan-details-ht-reports.html
Turkey’s banking regulator
requested that banks provide details of lending plans for each
of their branches and will demand that they’re revised should
targets exceed 25 percent, Haberturk newspaper reported without
saying where it got the information.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
